trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchema" /> class represents the schema partition for a particular domain.
trans-unit.target: La clase <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchema" /> representa la partición de esquema de un dominio determinado.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <see langword="false" /> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> para liberar tanto recursos administrados como no administrados; es <see langword="false" /> para liberar únicamente recursos no administrados.

trans-unit.source: Releases the managed resources that are used by the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchema" /> object and, optionally, releases unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: Libera los recursos administrados que el objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchema" /> utiliza y, de forma opcional, libera los recursos no administrados.

trans-unit.source: The `disposing` parameter affects only the release of managed resources.
trans-unit.target: El `disposing` parámetro sólo afecta a la liberación recursos administrados.

trans-unit.source: Unmanaged resources are always released by this method.
trans-unit.target: Este método libera siempre los recursos no administrados.
